# SuperDuo alexandria project

Info:

1. When application launched, Slide menu will show and Input Method will show in same time;
    I think this not a good feel, I will change it hide InputMethod window.

2. Application enter point is MainActivity

3. MainActivity uses drawer navigation.

4. Fragments:

    1) ListOfBooks  list books
    2) AddBook      add book or scan barcode
    3) About        about
    4) BookDetail   show book detail
    5) NavigationDrawerFragment   Android Studio default Drawer code.

5. Data support

    1) BookProvider       Provide book data query, insert support.
    2) DbHelper           SQLite database open support and tables define.
    3) AlexandriaContract BookProvider constants define.

6. Book support

    1) BookService Fetch book information with ISBN.

ChangeLog:

1. When MainActivity launched, InputMethod not show, if in list search page